ter=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976700/extras/ef5e049130474ee6faf75d206a5ad1f7.poster.avif?t=1772897462\" width=300 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976700/extras/ef5e049130474ee6faf75d206a5ad1f7.webm?t=1772897462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976700/extras/ef5e049130474ee6faf75d206a5ad1f7.mp4?t=1772897462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Once you collect three key ingredients, place them inside the antidote producer to produce an antidote!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976700/extras/26a11145f4f2095b2355c54205b2cd03.avif?t=1772897462\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br></li><li>When you shrink too small the game is over!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976700/extras/c3c6a474b516add83cc56de374ed5940.webp?t=1772897462\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tweak all kinds of settings, such as the height at which you start, how many double jumps you can do, or how long it takes for the Chemical Processor to complete its process! </li></ul>",
